actions.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.
Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

official_title: Excusing Mr. Edwards of California from serving as a manager for the trial of the impeachment of Alcee L. Hastings, judge of the United States District Court for the Southern District of Florida, and appointing Mr. Synar to serve as a manager in that trial.

summary.text: Excuses Representative Edwards, of California, from serving as a manager for the trial of the impeachment of Alcee L. Hastings, Judge of the U.S. District Court for the Southern District of Florida. Appoints Representative Synar to serve as a manager in such trial.
